data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the peaceful town of Menan, Idaho. This delightful residence at 625 N 3510 East offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. With its scenic surroundings, this property is sure to impress. The cozy living room is the ideal space for relaxation and quality time with loved ones, while the adjacent dining area provides a perfect setting for shared meals and entertaining guests. The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek countertops, ample cabinet storage, and a range of stainless steel appliances. This single level home also encompasses four generously sized bedrooms, each offering a peaceful retreat for rest and relaxation. The primary suite is a true haven, complete with a private en-suite bathroom, providing a luxurious escape from the demands of daily life. Step outside and discover a backyard oasis that's tailor-made for outdoor living. The expansive yard offers plenty of room for play, gardening, or hosting summer barbecues. Picture yourself enjoying the warm Idaho evenings on the patio. Enjoy the tranquility of small-town living while being just a short drive away from schools, shopping centers, dining establishments, and outdoor recreational opportunities.
